---
title: Chicken and Broccoli Stir-Fry with Green Onion Rice
description: Forget takeout because you can make drool-worthy Chinese-Canadian food from scratch! You'll caramelize chunks of chicken with a good sear, then toss them in a sweet and savoury honey-garlic sauce for a glossy finish! Tonight's accompaniments are classics: rice and broccoli.
